.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.postimg.org%2Fzzu52bwmn%2F1508057435505.png&h=f091cd9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由此可見，肥鳩大隻同本癲狗實力縣殊，想借本癲狗上位卻慘敗收場，因而只能作出零星而無力的反抗，反過來誣衊本癲狗借佢條傻鳩上位，其實本癲狗只係從容撚狗，已獲得大家支持</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>同時亦證明左，無論肥鳩大隻花盡心機，唸盡辦法想同本癲狗玩，但換黎既結果只有慘敗同被撚，所以永遠活係本癲狗既陰影之下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7c685091e40f8e01796146253be0ae84e8c4243c","tid":462220,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>肥絲大隻男人扮女人，鐵證如山，本癲狗發現左之後，知道原來自己係同緊一個變態人妖溝通，已懊悔不已，所以決定拆穿佢既罪行，免得各位受騙:</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>肥絲原來係肥佬扮肥婆!</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家唔知一定以為肥絲係女人啦, NO NO NO, 其實佢係男人黎, 睇下, 佢又自爆啦:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s22.postimg.org/i8z8gk3xt/Screenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs22.postimg.org%2Fi8z8gk3xt%2FScreenshot_2017-05-27-09-23-42.png&h=6a188dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人老狗幻想自己係女人都算啦, 但竟然幻想自已係肥矮臭柒毒既肥婆, 誤導各位, 真係又核突, 又變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過, 補充一點, 佢肥矮臭柒毒係事實, 不過係肥矮臭柒毒既麻甩佬, 並唔係肥婆囉.<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">快D用假膠黎掩飾啦傻鳩</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a0887ea98f99714540be1531a63b8e752e6b68","tid":462220,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T13:17:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;